text: Good laundry, i spend $6 for washing and $4 for dry 10kg. Very happy with the result. Will come back again.
Very clean place , machine was commercial type , very clean machine n fast drying..Even have music for you while waiting.
Great little spot for laundry. Reasonably priced and quick and a good wash
This LaundryMart Express where you guess it ,doing ðŸ§º laundromats and dry-cleaning. Pricing is quite reasonable .

Easy enough to use. The machines come with detergent and if you opt to pay a little more, there's softener too.

Dryer was a little confusing as there was a low, medium and high setting. Tried medium for 25 mins and my clothes were still a little damp*. An additional 10 mins of high temperature did the trick though I could have just use the high temp setting for 15 or 20 mins I think. So far no shrinkages.

If you change dollars to coins, there will be tokens, so plan ahead on the amount you might need.
